# The following commant runs the SConscript with the given arguments
# The first argument 'src/SConsrcipt' tells the address of the script to run. This file is where the build instruction are given. 
# The second argument 'variant_dir='obj'' tells where to place the built files (.o files) 
# The final argument requests Scons to not to duplicate the source files inside of obj 


SConscript('src/SConscript', variant_dir='obj',duplicate=0)


#For detailed instructions, refer "Separating Source and Build directories", Chapter 17, Scons user guide 2.0.1  
# https://scons.org/doc/2.0.1/HTML/scons-user/x3399.html
# and references given therein 




